WEBVTT

00:01:29.141 --> 00:01:31.501
holatiga kirganida 
maxsus molekulalarni

00:01:31.501 --> 00:01:34.351
sintez qila boshlaydi. Molekulalar 
hujayralarni to'ldirib,

00:01:34.351 --> 00:01:38.041
o'ziga xos matritsa hosil qilish orqali

00:01:38.041 --> 00:01:40.430
yo'qolgan suv o'rnini bosadi.

00:01:40.430 --> 00:01:43.080
Hujayraning quruqlikka sezgir
bo'lgan tarkibiy qismlari,

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:44.111
masalan, DNK,

00:01:44.111 --> 00:01:45.101
oqsillar

00:01:45.101 --> 00:01:46.191
va membranalar

00:01:46.191 --> 00:01:48.580
ushbu matritsaga qamaladi.

00:01:48.580 --> 00:01:51.973
Taxminlarga ko'ra, bu molekulalarni 
bir yerda to'plab, ularni

00:01:51.973 --> 00:01:53.631
yoyilib ketish,

00:01:53.631 --> 00:01:54.868
parchalanish yoki

00:01:54.868 --> 00:01:56.931
bir-biriga qo'shilib ketishdan saqlaydi.

00:01:56.931 --> 00:02:00.421
Tana suv ta'minotini 
to'ldirgandan so'ng, matritsa ochilib,